attributes.long-description: The hugely popular arcade and console fighting game, TEKKEN®5 DARK RESURRECTION™ is now available with an all-new ONLINE BATTLE feature! Take on other players from around the country, in full HD running at a smooth 60 frames per second! Prove who the real King of the Iron Fist Tournament is by checking the online rankings. Experience the pinnacle of fighting games as Tekken reaches into the “Online Vs.” world for the first time ever! The online features of TEKKEN®5 DARK RESURRECTION™ ONLINE make use of the PLAYSTATION®Network. All terms of use of the PLAYSTATION®Network apply. Online game play of TEKKEN®5 DARK RESURRECTION™ may be adversely affected by network conditions. As such, instances in which the game may not be playable online or the game play conditions suffer may occur. It is strongly recommended that the PLAYSTATION®3 computer entertainment system Internet Connection Test be successfully completed and the NAT Type be confirmed as 1 or 2 before playing this game. Please refer to the online PLAYSTATION®3 system online manual or the manual for your network equipment for information regarding network settings. The network service for TEKKEN®5 DARK RESURRECTION™ ONLINE may be ended at any time after prior notice on the product web page. http://www.namcobandaigames.com/games/tekken5dr/ Online ranking data lost for any reason will not be reinstated. Please refer to the online manual for information regarding the online service for TEKKEN®5 DARK RESURRECTION™ ONLINE. Note: “Online Vs.” matches are limited to matches between players of the same area.
